title: EVEN DON'T HAVE ENOUGH SPACE TO STORE STANDARD SIZE DRILL MACHINE
body: TRU REVIEW : Hello Guys, I have buy this from AMAZON, but after getting delivery I have returned it, due to small size , even doesn't have enough space to store a standard size drill machine or a medium size screw driver. If you are planning to store your regular size drill machine along with your other tools, then go for PTB19. Others wise you can buy it, if you don't have any drill machine. The build quality was too good. Lock and Handle was heavy. Overall body thickness was heavy.

title: 'Cheap Quality Material tool box by Taparia'
body: 'I purchased Taparia ptb16 from amazon on 26 dec. 2022 within 2 month 15 days i found a long crack in top upper body. Its a manufacturing defect. From my side no single scratch on the box. Taparia may be use cheap quality material in manufacturing or defective lot. I think local plastic container better than Taparia ptb 16 tool box. This is a zero star rating cheap quality product. Do not buy this product because no guarantee and no warranty on this tool box. I think local shopkeeper given gurantee on local container with good price.'
